Made a 30ml Tester and gave them 7 days to steep! Tested in a Kayfun V5, MTL, with simple spaced Coil. 1.5 Ohm and 20 Watts!&#xD;
What can i say what is not written in the other reviews.&#xD;
Its a great juice! Top balance of the flavours, a smooth and a full, tastefully vape. But not to pushy. &#xD;
All is there. A nice pastry, with a smooth, creamy filling. No dryness!  No need for a sweetener.&#xD;
If you like bakeries like me, it is a candidate for a Alldayvape.&#xD;
I have to look to mix some diffrent fillings. Its a great base too!&#xD;
Thanks for that great recipe @Goldfish18.

Wonderful. &#xD;
Rich and beautiful. &#xD;
Cures nicely and holds its flavor well over time. &#xD;
A real great recipe.
